<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 13:59:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>比特币价值 100 亿美元的期权到期风险加剧抛售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/bitcoin-s-woes-could-be-compounded-by-10-billion-options-expiry</link><description>比特币正面临大规模期权到期，这可能会给已经在机构需求减弱和宏观经济逆风中苦苦挣扎的市场带来更大压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i14rCG_hn7z4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 04:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-25/bitcoin-s-woes-could-be-compounded-by-10-billion-options-expiry</guid></item><item><title>Cantor SPAC 和 Adam Back DAT 之间的加密交易被推迟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/crypto-deal-between-cantor-spac-and-adam-back-dat-gets-delayed</link><description>备受关注的关于坎托·菲茨杰拉德关联公司与亚当·巴克领导的数字资产财务公司之间合作的投票已被推迟。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isCQTjUduxkE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 21:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/crypto-deal-between-cantor-spac-and-adam-back-dat-gets-delayed</guid></item><item><title>最大的加密货币买家望而却步，比特币再次跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-breaks-60-000-again-as-crypto-s-biggest-buyers-wobble</link><description>比特币跌回 60,000 美元以下，重新引发了过去两年加密货币领域基本没有的担忧：当市场最大买家面临压力而散户交易者失去兴趣时，会发生什么。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJOvnMXh864o/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-breaks-60-000-again-as-crypto-s-biggest-buyers-wobble</guid></item><item><title>比特币撤退的零售大军暴露出新的脆弱性</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-s-retreating-retail-army-exposes-fresh-market-fragility</link><description>比特币多年来一直试图摆脱其作为投机散户交易者游乐场的声誉。它最近的抛售暴露了这种权衡：华尔街带来了规模和合法性，但曾经帮助吸收急剧下跌的散户买家基本上消失了。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDWGM9hBqFxc/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 12:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-s-retreating-retail-army-exposes-fresh-market-fragility</guid></item><item><title>塞勒面临比特币困境，没有简单的出路</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/saylor-s-best-bet-may-be-to-halt-strategy-s-bitcoin-btc-buying-spree</link><description>迈克尔·塞勒(Michael Saylor)的比特币购买机器Strategy Inc.如果想恢复市场对其股票的信心，就应该停止购买这种加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCn0ThsHx9F0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 07:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/saylor-s-best-bet-may-be-to-halt-strategy-s-bitcoin-btc-buying-spree</guid></item><item><title>马特·达蒙重返数字资产世界</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-23/matt-damon-takes-a-journey-back-to-the-digital-asset-world</link><description>越来越多的迹象表明加密货币可能正在形成底部。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCKyBl.0AWt4/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-23/matt-damon-takes-a-journey-back-to-the-digital-asset-world</guid></item><item><title>科技股抛售引发避险情绪，比特币触及两周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-tech-selloff-sparks-risk-off-mood</link><description>由于科技股的抛售打击了风险资产，比特币跌至近两周低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iD6CSZF2Ssmo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 09:33:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-tech-selloff-sparks-risk-off-mood</guid></item><item><title>以太坊相关非营利组织在“充满挑战的时代”削减预算 40%</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ether-linked-nonprofit-cuts-budget-40-during-challenging-era</link><description>帮助创建世界第二大加密货币以太币底层技术的程序员维塔利克·布特林 (Vitalik Buterin) 表示，其背后的非营利组织正被迫做出一些艰难的决定。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqeD3m9kLhdQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 18:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ether-linked-nonprofit-cuts-budget-40-during-challenging-era</guid></item></channel></rss>